{"tid":466530,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【一周必看】 快到睇唔切！MMA拳手地標戰玩飛膝秒殺","createTime":"2017-11-12T15:44:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-13T05:06:54.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"bed2ab374fa7eef6acb930469b7c509763a3c374","tid":466530,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T15:44:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171112/20211662\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171112%2F20211662&d=Vwz5EBcLqWaBGEkS3GaoudU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=85a9b4b2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171112%2F20211662&h=c9613e73\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171112/20211662</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【一周必看】<br />\n快到睇唔切！MMA拳手地標戰玩飛膝秒殺<br />\n<br />\n6,419<br />\n<br />\n適中字型<br />\n較大字型<br />\n<br />\nMMA體壇爆出最強新人！現年24歲、來自美國克利夫蘭的羽量級選手Tywan Claxton，早前出戰自己首場MMA的職業生涯，想不到他竟然「平地一聲雷」，地標戰只用了不足90秒的時間，就用一招左腳飛膝擊中對手下顎，對方頓時應聲倒地沒有反應。不用拳證宣布勝負，Tywan Claxton已高興得跳上擂台的圍欄，與教練一起激動慶祝勝利，接受觀眾喝彩。<br />\n<br />\n相關的比賽片段隨即在網上瘋傳，不少網民均留言紛表驚訝。目前人氣急升的Tywan Claxton，已吸引到不少網民追蹤關注，不少人均期待下一場比賽，Tywan Claxton還有甚麼「殺手鐧」，能夠秒殺擂台上的對手呢？  <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n【一周必看】【投考AO攻略‧面試篇】考你EQ同反應　仲要認人夠精靈<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n【一周必看】強國單車手避車跌倒　發爛渣狂毆瑞士車隊"},{"pid":"7c284f57f419dfbc2738766b1dc8f4131ea267f8","tid":466530,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T15:59:11.000Z","msg":"Bellator 186: Tywan Claxton wins by Flying Knee Knockout!<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VirSoFoCUYE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DVirSoFoCUYE&d=Vwz5EBcLqWaBGEkS3GaoudU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=59bd99d3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VirSoFoCUYE</a>"},{"pid":"3a5c562b2ec090375c76499f872f0726f007eb91","tid":466530,"uid":41356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T16:37:50.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Tywan No.1</span></span>"},{"pid":"248f6ced07c70fcbac9b636f9e1377d5430e57f6","tid":466530,"uid":35910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T16:40:30.000Z","msg":"又係幾靚既"},{"pid":"eb36908bca2052101cf288e9872b33b30121357f","tid":466530,"uid":117628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T16:48:10.000Z","msg":"mma真係痴撚線運動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  唔係斷手斷腳就踢頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d3cea688540d749bf80a7b68fc026fe3947aedb","tid":466530,"uid":143774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T16:54:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>mma真係痴撚線運動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  唔係斷手斷腳就踢頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁先夠刺激<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87a339b72216b0a5e6bba8824017407fb346626f","tid":466530,"uid":40588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T21:57:57.000Z","msg":"Joe"},{"pid":"aac8647edd3739ff865cbefc220a849e6fb745cd","tid":466530,"uid":60333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T22:34:22.000Z","msg":"tiger knee <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cc9ec37188c615f075268cf85fe10454e4b22ab","tid":466530,"uid":31887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T04:50:53.000Z","msg":"個白皮豬廢姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n速度咁慢都暈<br />\n其實唔暈唔難"},{"pid":"e071c3855fce100be83fbde35cef875ad6af9dc5","tid":466530,"uid":42820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score